## Usage

Basic usage examples:

```bash
# Run the main script
uv run python main.py

# Run with specific parameters
uv run python main.py --option value
```

## Development

Install development dependencies:

```bash
uv add --dev pytest black ruff mypy
```

Run tests:

```bash
uv run pytest
```

Format code:

```bash
uv run black .
uv run ruff check .
```

